        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "light is less intense",
        "start": 162.4,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "but less so in the western us even",
        "start": 163.68,
        "duration": 4.559
    },
    {
        "text": "though the light there can be harsh plus",
        "start": 166.0,
        "duration": 3.92
    },
    {
        "text": "just because cold sunny days triggered",
