        "start": 169.92,
        "duration": 4.24
    },
    {
        "text": "there to deal with cold sunny conditions",
        "start": 172.0,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "at least that's what the proponents of",
        "start": 174.16,
        "duration": 3.68
    },
