        "text": "have evolved red leaves may be more",
        "start": 199.68,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "resistant to pests year round",
        "start": 201.44,
        "duration": 3.6
    },
    {
        "text": "though not all experts agree the big",
