        "text": "and for the same reason",
        "start": 236.799,
        "duration": 3.121
    },
    {
        "text": "some insect pests may have also gone",
        "start": 238.08,
        "duration": 3.84
    },
    {
        "text": "extinct which meant european trees",
        "start": 239.92,
        "duration": 3.28
    },
    {
        "text": "would have had less of a need for",
        "start": 241.92,
